Name: Local_Internal_Reference
Description: The Local_Internal_Reference class is used to cross-reference other classes or objects within the product.

Name: local_identifier_reference
Description: The local_identifier_reference attribute provides the value of the local_identifier of the entity described by the referencing class. Note that a local_identifier attribute, with the same value as this local_identifier_reference, must be present within the label.

Name: local_reference_type
Description: The local_reference_type attribute provides the name of an association between an entity identified by a local_identifier_reference and another corresponding entity identified by a local_identifier

Name: data_values_to_data_values
Description: A reference to the array containing data.

Name: comment
Description: The comment attribute is a character string expressing one or more remarks or thoughts relevant to the object.

Name: Data_Values
Description: The Data_Values class describes the values stored in a data array.

Name: Alternate_Values
Description: The Alternate_Values describes a direct one-to-one relationship of arrays of data values. Each data array must have the same dimensionality and number of elements.

Name: name
Description: The name attribute provides a word or combination of words by which the object is known.

Name: local_identifier
Description: The local_identifier attribute provides a character string which uniquely identifies the containing object within the label.

Name: description
Description: The description attribute provides a statement, picture in words, or account that describes or is otherwise relevant to the object.
